### List all users
GET http://localhost:3000/users HTTP/1.1

### List all posts
GET http://localhost:3000/posts HTTP/1.1

### Get published posts feed
GET http://localhost:3000/feed HTTP/1.1

### Get post by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/1 HTTP/1.1

### Create another user
POST http://localhost:3000/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "name": "Bob Smith"
}

### Create another user
POST http://localhost:3000/users HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@prisma.io",
  "name": "Alice"
}

### Create a new post
POST http://localhost:3000/posts HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Getting Started with Prisma",
  "content": "Prisma is a modern ORM that makes database access easy...",
  "authorEmail": "alice@prisma.io"
}

### Create another post
POST http://localhost:3000/posts HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Building REST APIs with Express",
  "content": "Express is a minimal and flexible Node.js web framework...",
  "authorEmail": "bob@example.com"
}

### Publish a post
PUT http://localhost:3000/posts/publish/2 HTTP/1.1

### Delete a post
DELETE http://localhost:3000/posts/2 HTTP/1.1